secubox-jitsi (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Complete rewrite with Docker-based deployment.
  * Features:
    - Docker-compose Jitsi stack (Web, Prosody, Jicofo, JVB, Jibri)
    - JWT, LDAP, and internal authentication support
    - Recording management via Jibri
    - Room statistics via JVB colibri API
    - P31 Phosphor light theme with teal accent
    - Comprehensive API for all Jitsi management
  * API Endpoints:
    - /health, /status - Health and status
    - /config - Configuration management
    - /rooms, /room/{name} - Room management
    - /stats - Server statistics
    - /recordings - Recording management
    - /auth/config - Authentication settings
    - /prosody/status - XMPP server status
    - /jibri/status, /enable, /disable - Recording service
    - /container/* - Docker lifecycle management
    - /logs - Container logs

 -- Gerald KERMA <devel@cybermind.fr>  Fri, 04 Apr 2026 09:00:00 +0100
